      <h3>test4:ezCalculate</h3>
      <p>打开ida,是简单的加密和计算</p>
      <p><img src="/img/posts/QCTF/ezc.png" alt="ezc" /></p>
      <p>直接逆向计算即可</p>
      <pre><code>#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;
int main()
{
    unsigned char key[22] = {
    0x77, 0x77, 0x71, 0x65, 0x73, 0x73, 0x67, 0x78, 0x73, 0x64, 0x64, 0x6B, 0x61, 0x61, 0x6F, 0x31, 
    0x32, 0x33, 0x77, 0x6D, 0x73,0x00
};
    unsigned char answer[22] = {
    0x33, 0x1D, 0x32, 0x44, 0x2A, 0x54, 0x45, 0x2C, 0x2E, 0x74, 0x8C, 0x4B, 0x40, 0x42, 0x43, 0x73, 
    0x71, 0x82, 0x24, 0x35, 0x10, 0x00, 
};
    for(int i=0;i&lt;21;i++)
    {
        answer[i]+=key[i];
    }
    for(int i=0;i&lt;21;i++)
    {
        
        answer[i]=answer[i]^key[i];
    }
    
    for(int i=0;i&lt;21;i++)
    {
        answer[i]-=key[i];
    }
    printf("%s",answer);
    
}
</code></pre>
      <pre><code>flag{Add_X0r_and_Sub}
</code></pre>
      <h3>test5:jvav</h3>
      <p>发现文件是apk格式，使用工具jadx，根据题目提示，我们发现EncKt</p>
      <p><img src="/img/posts/QCTF/jvav1.png" alt="jvav" /></p>
      <p>对明文主要处理为这一步</p>
      <p><img src="/img/posts/QCTF/jvav2.png" alt="jvav" /></p>
      <p>分别为：base64加密，相加异或取反，右移六位</p>
      <p>从外往里逆向计算即可</p>
      <pre><code>#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;
int main()
{
    short enc[]={-89, 96, 102, 118, -89, -122, 103, -103, -125, -95, 114, 117, -116, -102, 114, -115, -125, 108, 110, 118, -91, -83, 101, -115, -116, -114, 124, 114, -123, -87, -87, -114, 121, 108, 124, -114};
    short flag[36];
    for(int i=0;i&lt;36;i++)
    {
        flag[i]=enc[(i+31)%36];
    }
    for(int i=0;i&lt;36;i++)
    {
        flag[i]=((~flag[i])^11)-32;
    }
    for(int i=0;i&lt;36;i++)
    printf("%c",flag[i]);
}
</code></pre>
