</code></pre>
      <h3>test6:rand</h3>
      <p>观察到rand函数，我们可以留心找一下srand函数（用于生成伪随机数）</p>
      <p><img src="/img/posts/QCTF/rand1.png" alt="rand" /></p>
      <pre><code>#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;
#include &lt;stdlib.h&gt;
void swap(char *a,char *b)
{
    char temp=*a;
    *a=*b;
    *b=temp;
}
int main()
{
    int rands[1000];
    srand(12345);
    unsigned char enc[27] = {
    0x5A, 0x66, 0x86, 0xCE, 0x46, 0x23, 0x75, 0x30, 0x18, 0x6F, 0x5B, 0x7D, 0x4D, 0x4F, 0xF7, 0xC4, 
    0x4A, 0x0D, 0x45, 0xAE, 0x36, 0xEF, 0x6B, 0x81, 0xC1, 0x82, 0x03};
    for (int i = 0; i &lt; 256 * 2 + 27; i++) 
    {
    rands[i] = rand();
    printf("%d\n", rands[i]);
    }//获取一共用到的srand,前256*2个数用于交换,后27个数用于异或
    for (int i = 0; i &lt; 27; i++) 
    {
    enc[i] ^= rands[512 + i] & 0xFF;
    }//从下往上解，先异或
    for (int i = 256 * 2 - 1; i&gt;=0; i -= 2) {
    int z1 = rands[i] % 27;
    int z2 = rands[i - 1] % 27;
    swap(&enc[z1], &enc[z2]);
    }//从后往前交换，原程序中swap步骤是rand[0]到rand[256*2-1],这里为了恢复，应该从rand[256*2-1]开始逆交换
    for (int i = 0; i &lt; 27; i++)
    printf("%c", enc[i]);
    }
</code></pre>
      <p>注：文件为linux下程序，应在linux下编译并执行，不然srand有误</p>
